-- Iran Captures Foreign Drone Over Nation’s South, Fars Reports
-- B y   Z a i d   S a b a h
-- 2013-02-23T19:59:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-23/iran-captures-foreign-drone-over-nation-s-south-fars-reports.html
Iran  successfully captured a foreign
drone over the nation’s south, the Arabic service of the state-
run Fars news agency reported today.  Revolutionary Guards brought down the drone safely, Fars
said, citing a military official identified as Brigadier
Sarkhili.  More information will be disclosed later, Fars said. The
report didn’t specify what nation the drone belonged to.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zaid Sabah Abd Alhamid in Washington at 
 zalhamid@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
